In a true hustler spirit, Dj Sbu was at Bree Street in Joburg selling his energy drink at the robots on Wednesday morning. DJ Sbu is a known hustler whom together with the 3Sixty Financial Services Group,  launched The Hustlers Academy. He intends to develop
the minds and the ability of thousands of young hustlers in the country and
change lives. He tweeted: "Today I will do what others won’t, so tomorrow I can accomplish what others can’t.

Lead by example when you're an entrepreneur, both for your team and for your customers." 